    {
      "instruction": "<p><strong>Reduce</strong> the heat to medium-low and cook for 5-7min or until everything is piping hot and tender</p>\r\n<p>Tip: The stock and starch from the beans make a creamy yet thin sauce, so don't evaporate the stock completely</p>\r\n<p><strong>Taste</strong> and tweak for seasoning</p>",
